      "raw_text": "The incorporation of trades unions\nwill in all probability not materialize\nin Spokane. The example of the labor\nbodies in Portland does not meet with\nfavor here.\n\n\nThe American Federation of Labor\nhas taken the subject under consid-\nGrafton, although Clarence Darrow\nsounds the following note of warn\ning:\n\n\nthat could keep out of the hands of\na court for one year if it ever con-\nscented to become incorporated."
